{"tid":162113,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋細個老師講書講錯野你哋會點回應","createTime":"2017-03-19T04:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T05:03:59.000Z","uid":80481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f65fd29dbc44cd9ae02d91586880bcf71cbeb79","tid":162113,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"以前小學睇嗰隻商務新詞典 ,入面有啲詞語、成詞都幾得意就成日揭，有一次常識老師教中國，問我哋中國有邊啲少數民族，其他同學睇書就答普通嗰啲滿族、壯族啊嗰啲，我諗起詞典有寫水族係少數民族，就即刻舉手答諗住實比老師讚啦，點知佢話冇個咁嘅族，比全班笑9我(可能以為係我玩，講水族館嗰啲) ,之後睇返書條氣好唔順都冇辦法"},{"pid":"08c8d6172251820e6f1880bd6be7dd242dbcf4dd","tid":162113,"uid":90390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"細個我會好唔開心，同老師頂嘴，之後俾人罰。<br />\n大個知道指鹿為馬既故事，學習左秦朝大臣既智慧。<br />\n唔好講上司，就算同事朋友之間都要指鹿為馬，都唔好得罪人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b775bdfba4c4d3c89aa746cb712c3afd37a9799","tid":162113,"uid":9758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個我會好唔開心，同老師頂嘴，之後俾人罰。<br />\n大個知道指鹿為馬既故事，學習左秦朝大臣既智慧。<br />\n唔好講上司，就算同事朋友之間都要指鹿為馬，都唔好得罪人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出到嚟的確要咁.. 想講自己嘅睇法<br />\n得 你上咗位先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c335b0c0ae1fb543284f653d72b09ed3d9822ed9","tid":162113,"uid":90390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個我會好唔開心，同老師頂嘴，之後俾人罰。<br />\n大個知道指鹿為馬既故事，學習左秦朝大臣既智慧。<br />\n唔好講上司，就算同事朋友之間都要指鹿為馬，都唔好得罪人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出到嚟的確要咁.. 想講自己嘅睇法<br />\n得 你上咗位先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYES，當然上左位如非必要都唔好講實話。<br />\n老師係權威，就算佢講錯野，只要無傷大雅，都唔好頂撞。<br />\n萬一方丈好小氣，覺得你落佢臉，以後就大鑊。<br />\n開頭唔爽搵野罰你，再見你善良唔反抗，以後有咩事都捉來殺雞警猴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ef2557aac381c507214c68326ed4e85edd7248","tid":162113,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:09:20.000Z","msg":"以前細細個有個幼稚園老師話鱷魚係海洋生物，跟住我話鱷魚係生活係沼澤到，跟住老師話我駁嘴要見家長<br />\n老母撐我，之後就成日就比班老師針對到幼稚園畢業（好彩係高班）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc9ef2f328e2979ebb04a1a95dd693a3d322e6c","tid":162113,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前細細個有個幼稚園老師話鱷魚係海洋生物，跟住我話鱷魚係生活係沼澤到，跟住老師話我駁嘴要見家長<br />\n老母撐我，之後就成日就比班老師針對到幼稚園畢業（好彩係高班）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係老師都唔會認自己連幼稚園學生都不如啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d8069ca82b2f492ea55b955e6808de4a1dd32f","tid":162113,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"小學仲有一次但唔係老師嘅問題，佢問我哋公元紀年喺點計，我嗰時睇某本科普漫畫睇過係耶穌出生之後，講出嚟即刻比全班笑，好彩之後老師還我清白"},{"pid":"035db85fc389a079fb074fc8d9bcf83708177462","tid":162113,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前細細個有個幼稚園老師話鱷魚係海洋生物，跟住我話鱷魚係生活係沼澤到，跟住老師話我駁嘴要見家長<br />\n老母撐我，之後就成日就比班老師針對到幼稚園畢業（好彩係高班）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係老師都唔會認自己連幼稚園學生都不如啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以真係話 無常識同蠢既唔好做老師<br />\n害死下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83088f19463b9ab5a1e82ad22296b8a797df4880","tid":162113,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd1e5f13061a18129ee788ab05bcd03f0f44f37","tid":162113,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前細細個有個幼稚園老師話鱷魚係海洋生物，跟住我話鱷魚係生活係沼澤到，跟住老師話我駁嘴要見家長<br />\n老母撐我，之後就成日就比班老師針對到幼稚園畢業（好彩係高班）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係老師都唔會認自己連幼稚園學生都不如啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以真係話 無常識同蠢既唔好做老師<br />\n害死下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得老師唔係要乜都識<br />\n唔識唔緊要<br />\n錯完一次咪記得<br />\n最重要都係虛心求教 不斷學習<br />\n唔好覺得學生識 自己唔識就冇面"},{"pid":"66e75ffc706381c607e4c904bfb343efb151b673","tid":162113,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"唔回應 [wfc]"},{"pid":"578a9607f4df092894b933a6ab1a5ef46a48b232","tid":162113,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"細個小五我唔知寫咩功課，話中國係1966年開始文化大革命，個MISS死都要話1967（佢仲要年紀唔細，計返都應該四五十年代出世），我就拎本會考中史書返去話係1966，佢就好唔順氣咁話，哦咁咪1966囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60068b42144e7dc74fd3c546009dbe62e804995b","tid":162113,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔聽書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非考試測驗改錯我，唔係唔會出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da82bde41127235e77eaff6f7c0da82277db955","tid":162113,"uid":62061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"幼稚園老師知識水平一定係低過中小學老師<br />\n不過唔認錯真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb1f9de00ba5157bd7dbc9996ee7ce899e784b1","tid":162113,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幼稚園老師知識水平一定係低過中小學老師<br />\n不過唔認錯真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得最離譜有一次，幼稚園個同學仔擧手提到差人呢個詞，跟住個on9 miss話：唔係差人！係警察！差人係嗰啲差差下既人<br />\n我諗左廿年都唔知咩叫差差下既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63191038874ac07e1f019710987349211a4b41be","tid":162113,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幼稚園老師知識水平一定係低過中小學老師<br />\n不過唔認錯真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得最離譜有一次，幼稚園個同學仔擧手提到差人呢個詞，跟住個on9 miss話：唔係差人！係警察！差人係嗰啲差差下既人<br />\n我諗左廿年都唔知咩叫差差下既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n衙差個差<br />\n不過有學識就唔使教幼稚園啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ae174d75bdd0cc5c80abbab09e200b222d5152","tid":162113,"uid":74828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:20:50.000Z","msg":"屌 小學果時 常識政府部門<br />\n佢list 左幾個部門標誌出黎叫我地答<br />\n問到我 佢指左路政署要我答 <br />\n咁多咪答路政署囉 點知佢話係運輸署<br />\n屌 我老豆做路政架嘛 我點會答佢 但佢死都話我錯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8528c945ffaa24526f15d71edc6a12660c898940","tid":162113,"uid":29247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"小學中文老師話香港係南半球<br />\n明明我一直都記得係北半球<br />\n佢又好撚堅持肯定係南半球仲要語氣好惡咁覺得我搞事<br />\n搞到後尾我同其他人講香港係南半球然後被人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fedbaedeb1d217c662aa7325fa94893f56256e7","tid":162113,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幼稚園老師知識水平一定係低過中小學老師<br />\n不過唔認錯真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得最離譜有一次，幼稚園個同學仔擧手提到差人呢個詞，跟住個on9 miss話：唔係差人！係警察！差人係嗰啲差差下既人<br />\n我諗左廿年都唔知咩叫差差下既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能佢想講係女媧造人用泥搓(差)出嚟嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab890bfcf140e3b45fd34b1fe90e6017f93bbd4","tid":162113,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acdadeb3090f5c05e5217a835c6f1a11a218eaa","tid":162113,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學中文老師話香港係南半球<br />\n明明我一直都記得係北半球<br />\n佢又好撚堅持肯定係南半球仲要語氣好惡咁覺得我搞事<br />\n搞到後尾我同其他人講香港係南半球然後被人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌睇完你講先知香港係北半球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40a64f100dcd5a42083b75ce6692ed32066afdc","tid":162113,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲唔聽書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非考試測驗改錯我，唔係唔會出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係有時無聊得濟望下黑版寫咩，就見到佢寫錯野，好難唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44fa9151fe5d522819ee32e0335d5c88f486759","tid":162113,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}